Description:
    Install the Bug-Fab Rails Engine into the host application.

    Creates `config/initializers/bug_fab.rb` showing every configurable
    option and a sane default. The engine's migrations are picked up by
    the host's `db:migrate` automatically — no separate copy step is
    required.

Example:
    bin/rails generate bug_fab:install

    Then:
        bin/rails db:migrate
        # And add to config/routes.rb:
        #   mount BugFab::Engine, at: "/bug-fab"
